CHROMEVOX_READ_LINK_URL.message: Announce the URL behind a link

CHROMEVOX_POWER_KEY_HELP.message: Press up or down to review commands, press enter to activate

CHROMEVOX_GUESS_ROW_HEADER.message: Make a guess at the row header of the current cell

CHROMEVOX_SKIP_TO_ROW_END.message: Go to end of the current row

CHROMEVOX_SKIP_TO_COL_BEGINNING.message: Go to beginning of the current column

CHROMEVOX_OPTIONS_OUTPUT_CONTEXT_FIRST.message: Display an item's context before other information (such as its name).

CHROMEVOX_OPTIONS_CURSOR_BETWEEN_CHARACT.message: Place cursor between characters when editing text (like Mac OS X).

CHROMEVOX_OPTIONS_VOICES_DESCRIPTION.message: Change the current voice by selecting an option from the list below.

CHROMEVOX_CHOICE_WIDGET_HELP.message: Use up and down arrow keys to browse, or type to search.

CHROMEVOX_SEARCH_HELP_ITEM.message: Press enter to accept or escape to cancel, down for next and up for previous.

CHROMEVOX_TOGGLE_EARCONS.message: Turn sound feedback (earcons) on or off.
